6
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,239
You just now, this sign...

7
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,200
...was not here, okay?

8
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:21,000
What?

9
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:21,879
Were you just...

10
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:22,879
...taking it out from inside?

11
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:23,319
Excuse me.

12
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,040
No.

13
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:24,959
See? Look.

14
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,159
He's perfectly fine.

15
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:27,280
Don't talk nonsense.

16
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,879
If the boss finds out, I'll get fined.

17
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,879
Watch where you're going.

18
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:33,239
Why are you looking at your phone?

19
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,239
I already told you.

20
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:38,159
You just wouldn't believe me.

21
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,200
So what could I do?

22
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,000
How could I have known?

23
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,719
I really don't get it.

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,000
Better luck next time.

25
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,959
Stop. The interview just ended.

26
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,280
I don't know what to say.

27
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,040
He started by asking my salary expectation.

28
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,879
I've never been to Shenzhen before.

29
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,319
And I've never done sales.

30
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:02,200
And I've only been here a few days.

31
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,840
So of course I didn't know.

32
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:06,159
What do you think?

33
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,039
I know.

34
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,879
But last month...

35
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,319
...you got eighty points, right?

36
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,479
How come it's only seventy this month?

37
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,919
What's going on?

38
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,039
What do you mean, "what's going on"?

39
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:16,199
This is what's going on.

40
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,159
And let me tell you...

41
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,400
...the other candidates just now...

42
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,960
...all had at least a bachelor's degree.

43
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,719
