44
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,840
I'll hang out for a couple days and go back.

45
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:22,960
It's such a trivial thing.

46
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,039
And you're already crestfallen.

47
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,400
The worst part is...

48
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:27,759
...this morning...

49
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,879
