50
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,479
A cleaning lady...

51
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,479
Forget it.

52
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,560
She wouldn't admit it anyway.

53
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,360
Alright.

54
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,680
A bad workman blames his tools.

55
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:37,479
Gotta go.

56
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,120
Here.

57
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:57,800
