170
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,680
There's overtime pay for Spring Festival.

171
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:23,279
Besides, after the holiday,

172
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:24,040
I'll go back.

173
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:24,839
Thanks.

174
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,120
