175
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:27,160
Going back to Harbin.

176
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,040
My son is about to take the college entrance exam.

177
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,639
At a time like this,

178
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,800
