179
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:32,959
What about his father?

180
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,279
He's been gone for many years.

181
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:36,199
After this meal,

182
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,399
