207
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,279
Li Lei.

208
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,399
Don't forget.

209
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:23,800
Li Lei! Li Lei!

210
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,279
Hou Sai Lei!

211
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,480
No problem.

212
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:28,319
